text: The Sienne (fr) is a river in France. Sienne may refer to the following: ==Places== *Canton of Quettreville-sur-Sienne, French canton *Gavray-sur- Sienne, French commune *Heugueville-sur-Sienne, French commune *Noues de Sienne, French commune *Orval-sur-Sienne, French commune *Quettreville-sur- Sienne, French commune *Tourville-sur-Sienne, French commune ==People== *Aldebrandin de Sienne, alternate name of Aldebrandin of Siena *Catherine de Sienne, alternate name of Catherine of Siena ==See also== *Siena, an Italian town, and Siena_(disambiguation) *Sienna, a clay or a pigment, and Sienna_(disambiguation) *Seine, a river in France, and Seine_(disambiguation)
title: Sienne
